## Migration Checklist

When moving content from theory to experiments:
- [ ] Copy content to new location
- [ ] Add forward reference in theory chapter
- [ ] Add backward reference in experiments chapter
- [ ] Update cross-references (\ref{} labels)
- [ ] Verify theorem dependencies still satisfied
- [ ] Update table of contents if needed
- [ ] Recompile document to check references
- [ ] Remove original content from theory chapter
- [ ] Update any citations to moved content

